      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LITTLE GIRL GONE (2) has a strong record this track and trip with five wins and three placings from 15 starts. Recorded a half a length win (17.05) in a Grade 4 last time at this track. Rates a leading player. ROYAL CAROL (1) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 6th at this track following on from a second place finish (17.09) there the start prior. Solid record here at the distance winning 12 races. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Likely to be thereabouts. RISKY SPECIAL (3) goes very well this course and distance starting 16 times for six wins and six minors. Placed last time (17.08) at this track in a Grade 4, finishing second and beaten half a length. Makes strong appeal on best. NEEDLE AND SEAT (7) has claims fresh from a recent placing.",
